Workout Routine
There will be 5 set 
Warm-Up (5-10 minutes): Light cardio (jogging, skipping, or dynamic stretches).
Workout
Squats – 3 sets of 12 reps
Push-ups – 3 sets of 10-12 reps (modify on knees if needed)
Dumbbell Rows – 3 sets of 10 reps per arm
Plank – 3 sets of 30-60 seconds
Deadlifts (with or without weights) – 3 sets of 12 reps
Cool-Down: Stretch major muscle groups for 5-10 minutes.
